  "optimization_hints": [
    "Q1: Fully parallelize lineitem scan with morsel-driven execution (64 cores): 59M rows, L3 cache = 44MB, divide into ~4000-5000 morsels of 10-15K rows. Use vectorized filtering on l_shipdate, then partial aggregation per morsel with compact hash tables (6 groups). Final merge is negligible.",
